						activities to help you achieve your goals, and act as a supervisor to the 
						training and encouragement needed to stay the course.  
						Hiring a trainer is a commitment that you are making to yourself 
						and in doing so, you are re-enforcing your commitment to achieve
						your goals. 
					</p>
					<p>
