						trying to accomplish in this workout and this can occur with the help 
						of a trainer.  A trainer can help you develop a good training routine that is 
						designed to fit your needs, based on your time availability, fitness 
						level, and many other factors.  They will help you understand 
						why you are doing the training and the specific workouts you are 
						doing.  Your understanding of the process of training should help 
						your training become more efficient, as you will know the purpose 
